    "title": "Logos — \"The Word\"",
    "description": "When the prophet speaks, it is not mere speech. It is the Word of the Lord—logos carrying the force of creation, judgment, and truth. In the New Testament, Jesus is called the Logos, the Word made flesh. The prophet Elijah speaks that same Word when he confronts Ahab. The Word of God accomplishes what it sets out to do.",
