    "title": "I Forced Myself — The Language of Self-Override",
    "description": "Saul uses a word that reveals his inner state. He did not slip into the act unconsciously. He did not stumble or fall. He \"forced\" himself. He overrode his own conscience to act. He knew it was not his place. He did it anyway. This is not a mistake. It is a choice.",
    "bookSlug": "1-samuel",
