    "title": "No Smith — אֵין חָרָשׁ",
    "description": "The smith was the master of the most advanced technology of the age—the ability to work metal into useful form. Without a smith, a nation has no weapons, no tools of war. Israel is technologically and militarily isolated.",
    "bookSlug": "1-samuel",
    "chapter": 13,
    "language": "hebrew"
