    "title": "Nicham — Repented, Grieved",
    "description": "This is the word used when God looks at what He has made and grieves over it. It is not the word for changing one&apos;s mind in the sense of lacking foresight. It is the word for the grief of watching something or someone you love turn away from the path you set for them.",
    "bookSlug": "1-samuel",
