    "title": "Strength of Israel — God&apos;s Permanence",
    "description": "This title refers to God as the eternal, unchanging strength of Israel. The word <em>netzach</em> can mean both strength and eternity. The point is clear: God is not like a man, who repents, who changes His mind, who wavers. God&apos;s word stands. What He has said cannot be unsaid.",
