    "title": "Mashach — To Anoint",
    "description": "Anointing with oil is an act of consecration and setting apart. It marks someone as chosen, as claimed by God, as belonging to Him. The oil is poured, the person is marked, and from that moment forward they are no longer ordinary — they are set apart for a divine purpose.",
