    "description": "When David caught the lion by its beard, he grabbed hold of the thing that marks a creature&apos;s power and dignity. To catch something by the beard is to seize it at the point of its strength. David is not speaking theoretically. He has faced beasts that would kill a man, and he has prevailed.",
