    "title": "Adialeiptos — &ldquo;Without Ceasing&rdquo;",
    "description": "Prayer without ceasing is a life posture, not a task. It is the unbroken communion of the believer with God—maintained even while sleeping, working, speaking, and resting.",
    "bookSlug": "1-thessalonians",
