    "title": "Parousia — &ldquo;Coming&rdquo;",
    "description": "Parousia originally meant the arrival or visit of a king or dignitary. In the NT it denotes Christ&apos;s future appearing in power and glory. It is not a private event but a cosmic, public manifestation.",
