    "title": "Sotēria — &ldquo;Salvation&rdquo;",
    "description": "Salvation is not escape from the world but rescue from judgment and union with Christ. It is the central gift of the gospel—not what we earn but what Christ procures and gives.",
    "bookSlug": "1-thessalonians",
