    "script": "ἀγάπη",
    "translit": "<strong>agapē</strong> · selfless love; the love of God toward us",
    "title": "Agapē — Love",
    "description": "Not sentimental affection (philos) but the sacrificial, others-centered love that lays down its own interests. This is the kind of love Christ demonstrated on the cross—unconditional, costly, freely given.",
    "bookSlug": "1-timothy",
    "chapter": 1,
    "language": "greek"
