    "script": "ὑποτύπωσις",
    "translit": "<strong>hupotyposis</strong> · pattern; example; sketch; outline set before us",
    "title": "Hupotyposis — Pattern, Example, Outline",
    "description": "Paul&apos;s transformation is not a one-off miracle but a template. His life becomes a pattern—a living example—for everyone who comes after him. If Christ&apos;s longsuffering could change Paul the persecutor, it can change anyone.",
