    "translit": "<strong>nephalios</strong> · clear-minded; free from addiction; temperate",
    "title": "Nephalios — \"Vigilant\"",
    "description": "The word means more than mere sobriety (though that is part of it). It is clarity of mind, the opposite of the fog that comes from wine, drugs, or obsession. A leader must think straight.",
