    "translit": "<strong>eusebeia</strong> · reverence toward God; piety; devotion",
    "title": "Eusebeia — \"Godliness\"",
    "description": "Eusebeia is not mere religious correctness. It is reverence that flows from knowing God and being shaped by that knowledge. The mystery of godliness is that God, who is invisible and infinite, has made Himself known in Christ.",
    "bookSlug": "1-timothy",
    "chapter": 3,
    "language": "greek"
