    "translit": "<strong>apokrima</strong> · answer, response, verdict, judgment",
    "title": "Apokrima — &ldquo;Sentence&rdquo;; Judicial Verdict",
    "description": "A legal term: the pronouncement of a court. Paul carries an internal death sentence. He has been judged and condemned by the weight of his circumstances. But this very sentence drives him away from himself and toward God.",
