    "description": "In a business transaction, the arrabōn is a deposit given as guarantee that the full payment will follow. The Holy Spirit is God&apos;s guarantee: the down payment that the full inheritance will be delivered. He is not all of what is promised, but He is real, He is precious, and He is the promise kept in miniature.",
    "bookSlug": "2-corinthians",
