    "translit": "<strong>Em</strong> · mother; source; origin",
    "title": "Em — \"mother\"",
    "description": "The mother in this vision is Jerusalem Zion, the city of God, now transformed into a nursing mother for all nations. She is not destroyed but enlarged, her maternal love extending beyond the ethnic Israel to all who believe.",
