    "title": "Chesed — \"Mercy\" or \"Covenant Love\"",
    "description": "Throughout this recounting, chesed is the connecting thread. God does not abandon the seed of Adam; He keeps covenant with Abraham; He preserves Israel. Not because they deserve it, but because He is chesed—faithful to His word.",
