    "translit": "<strong>aion</strong> · age; era; a period of time with its own character",
    "title": "Aion—Age",
    "description": "The present age is characterized by the reign of that evil seed. But <em>aion</em> means it is not the only age. Other ages have existed or will exist. The present age has a boundary.",
