    "title": "Semeion—Sign",
    "description": "A sign is not an accident. It is a deliberate marker, placed by God, to wake the sleeping and to orient the faithful toward what is coming. When you see the signs Uriel describes, you are meant to recognize them.",
    "bookSlug": "2-esdras",
    "chapter": 4,
