    "title": "Telos—End; Purpose",
    "description": "The end is not mere cessation. It is the <em>telos</em>—the fulfillment of purpose, the moment when all the scattered pieces resolve into their intended whole. This is not something Ezra can calculate. But it is fixed. It is coming.",
