    "description": "David returned \"in peace\" — in shalom. For Mephibosheth, this shalom means David is alive, is whole, has returned safely. It is not political peace. It is the peace of a man whose lord is safe. And Mephibosheth has waited in the wilderness of not-knowing, unwashed, unshaven, until that shalom came.",
