    "description": "The suffix <em>-ianos</em> means \"belonging to\" or \"follower of.\" A <em>christianos</em> is someone who belongs to Christ. The name is likely given by outsiders who observed the believers&apos; absolute allegiance to Christ. It sticks because it is true.",
