    "translit": "<strong>limos</strong> · famine; widespread hunger; severe lack",
    "title": "Limos — Famine; Hunger; Extreme Scarcity",
    "description": "A famine is not mere shortage. It is crisis. Starvation. The word carries weight. When Agabus speaks, he is speaking of suffering to come. And the church&apos;s response will be immediate.",
