    "script": "מָן",
    "translit": "<strong>man</strong> · manna, the dew-food from heaven",
    "title": "Man — &ldquo;manna&rdquo;",
    "description": "The word itself contains a question: in Exodus, the people ask &ldquo;Man hu?&rdquo; — &ldquo;What is it?&rdquo; Manna is food whose origin and nature the eaters must ask about. It cannot be taken for granted; it must be received daily with gratitude and wonder.",
