    "translit": "<strong>navi</strong> · one who speaks for God, the mouth of God",
    "title": "Navi — &ldquo;prophet&rdquo;",
    "description": "A prophet is not a fortune-teller. He is the one chosen by God to carry His word. His speech is God&apos;s speech. He speaks what God commands.",
