    "title": "Gevul — \"Boundary, Landmark\"",
    "description": "The gevul marks what belongs to whom. To move it is not a minor infraction; it is to rewrite the order God established. Every family was given land as their inheritance in Canaan. The landmarks protected that gift from the strong stealing from the weak.",
