    "title": "Cherem — &ldquo;devoted destruction&rdquo;",
    "description": "Cherem appears also in the fall of Jericho (Joshua 6) and in the warning against coveting plundered idols. It is sacred destruction—not wanton, but purposeful, an instrument of God&apos;s judgment wielded by His people in His service.",
