    "title": "Yare — &ldquo;afraid&rdquo;",
    "description": "The same root appears in Proverbs 9:10: &ldquo;The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom.&rdquo; Here, the call is to transfer fear—away from the enemy, toward God. One fear must be broken by a greater one.",
