    "translit": "<strong>kedesha</strong> · a consecrated prostitute",
    "title": "Kedesha — &ldquo;sacred prostitute&rdquo;",
    "description": "In Canaanite temples, sexual acts were offered as a form of worship. Israel is to have no such thing. The body is not a tool for religious ritual or economic exploitation.",
