    "script": "קֹדֶשׁ",
    "translit": "<strong>qodesh</strong> · consecrated, belonging to God alone",
    "title": "Qodesh — &ldquo;set apart&rdquo;",
    "description": "The firstborn are not dedicated to God as an afterthought — they are qodesh, permanently set apart, like the temple or the altar. They belong to Him in a category of their own.",
