    "script": "פָּרֹכֶת",
    "translit": "<strong>parokhet</strong> · a barrier, a curtain that separates",
    "title": "Parokhet — &ldquo;veil&rdquo;",
    "description": "The parokhet is not a mere divider. It is the specific curtain mentioned in verse 31 that will hang between the Holy Place and the Holy of Holies. It defines the limit of approach. It is the threshold no one may pass.",
    "bookSlug": "exodus",
