    "title": "Kofer — &ldquo;ransom&rdquo;",
    "description": "Kofer appears throughout Scripture: a ransom paid to save a life (Ex. 21:30), atonement money, or the covering that makes peace between God and humanity. It is the word for both the price and the pardon.",
