    "title": "Adamah - &ldquo;ground&rdquo;",
    "description": "The wordplay from chapter 2 returns and turns dark. The man (<em>adam</em>) was made from the ground (<em>adamah</em>). Now the ground itself is cursed for his sake. There is no part of human existence - not body, not work, not relationship, not the very dirt under the feet - that the Fall does not touch.",
