    "description": "The cherubim will reappear at the entrance of the tabernacle (Ex. 26:31) and embroidered into the curtain of the holy of holies. Eden was the first holy place; from now on every place where God dwells will be guarded the same way. When Jesus dies, that curtain - the one with the cherubim on it - is torn from top to bottom (Matt. 27:51). The guarded way is open again.",
