    "translit": "<strong>Bethel</strong> · house of God",
    "title": "Bethel - &ldquo;house of God&rdquo;",
    "description": "Bethel is where Abram first built an altar to the LORD after leaving Haran. Returning here is a deliberate turning toward God. The place itself is a landmark, a sacred geography of his own making.",
