    "translit": "<strong>beit-el</strong> · house of God",
    "title": "Beit-El - &ldquo;house of God&rdquo;",
    "description": "Bethel is not a house made with hands. It is the place where heaven touches earth, where the infinite God met a terrified man on a stone and made a covenant. Across Scripture, when people return to Bethel, it is to remember that encounter - to stand in the place where God was, and to be transformed.",
    "bookSlug": "genesis",
