    "script": "שִׁבְעִים",
    "translit": "<strong>shib&apos;im</strong> · seven times ten; completion, all nations",
    "title": "Shib&apos;im - \"seventy\"",
    "description": "In biblical numerology, 70 represents totality and wholeness - the number of Israel&apos;s elders, the number of the nations, the number of years of exile before restoration. Israel descends to Egypt in the form of the nations themselves.",
    "bookSlug": "genesis",
