    "script": "יתר",
    "translit": "<strong>yeter</strong> · excess, advantage, surplus; the portion that marks you as first",
    "title": "Yeter - &ldquo;excellence, preeminence&rdquo;",
    "description": "Reuben will not have the \"excess\" - the extra blessing and authority that belongs to the firstborn. Someone else will rise above him.",
    "bookSlug": "genesis",
