    "title": "Emunah — \"Faith\"",
    "description": "The Hebrew word \"emunah\" is closely related to \"amen\"—it means constancy, reliability, steadfast trust. It is not mere belief, but a trust that endures, that does not waver even when circumstances seem to justify wavering.",
