    "script": "שׂוּם",
    "translit": "<strong>Sumu</strong> · to set; to consider; to place",
    "title": "Sumu — \"Consider\"",
    "description": "The Hebrew word means to set your mind on something, to give it your attention. Haggai is calling the people to think carefully about the consequences of their choices.",
