    "title": "Cherev — \"Sword\"",
    "description": "The sword is girded at the side of every builder. It is not a symbol of distrust in God — it is an instrument of obedience to the call to both faith and vigilance. The sword does not contradict the trowel. It protects the work that the trowel accomplishes.",
