    "title": "Cherpah — \"Reproach\" or \"Shame\"",
    "description": "Cherpah is not merely embarrassment — it is shame that clings, that damages honor, that marks a person or community as unworthy. Nehemiah&apos;s prayer asks that the cherpah leveled against his people be turned back on those who leveled it.",
