    "title": "Gadol — \"Great\"",
    "description": "The Lord is gadol — not merely in size or power, but in significance and authority. He is the Great One. All other powers are subordinate to Him. When Nehemiah calls the people to \"remember the Lord, which is great,\" he is calling them to set their fear in proper perspective. The Lord is greater than Sanballat. He is greater than the army of the Ammonites. He is greater than death itself.",
