    "title": "Kowach — \"Strength\" or \"Power\"",
    "description": "The strength of the workers is failing. Not because they have less food or rest, but because fear is consuming their capacity to believe they can finish the work. Kowach is not merely physical — it is the power to persist, to hope, to keep moving toward a goal.",
