    "title": "אֱמוּנָה — Emunah",
    "description": "Hananiah&apos;s faithfulness is the Hebrew emunah — not mere sincerity, but the steady, dependable character that holds fast under pressure. Emunah is what makes a person worthy of trust in the eyes of heaven and earth. It is the quality that endures.",
