    "description": "The register speaks of \"the congregation\" — kahal in Hebrew, the assembled people bound together by covenant. This is not simply a census. It is a reckoning of the covenant community, those who have answered the call to return and rebuild. To be counted is to be bound to the people and its destiny.",
