    "title": "Goral — &ldquo;Lot&rdquo;",
    "description": "The Hebrew word goral carries the sense of both chance and divine intention. When you cast the lot, you are placing the decision into God&apos;s hands. It is the mechanism by which the invisible will becomes visible.",
