    "title": "Ir haqqodesh — &ldquo;The Holy City&rdquo;",
    "description": "Jerusalem is not merely a city; it is the holy city. Every person — from the overseer of the Levites to the Nethinims, from the priests to the singers — finds a place within this holiness. Nothing is outside the sacred. All are part of the restoration.",
    "bookSlug": "nehemiah",
