    "title": "Nadav — &ldquo;Willing Offering&rdquo;",
    "description": "The verb nadav appears throughout Scripture for those who volunteer their service, their resources, their lives. To nadav is to say: I will do this, not because I must, but because I choose to consecrate myself to something holy.",
