    "title": "Levi — &ldquo;attached, joined to&rdquo;",
    "description": "The tribe of Levi bears the name of a different kind of belonging. Not mustered for war, but attached to the work of the tabernacle. Different calling, different number, same knowledge — the Levites are still known, still seen.",
