    "title": "Anan — \"Cloud\"",
    "description": "The Shekinah—the dwelling-glory of God made visible. By day it rests as cloud over the tabernacle; by night it becomes fire. The same presence; two forms. A pillar that speaks. Israel does not choose when to move; the cloud chooses.",
