    "title": "Pesach Sheni — \"Second Passover\"",
    "description": "One month later. The exact ordinances, the exact meat, the exact herbs—everything the first Passover carries, the second Passover carries too. But it is marked with the word \"second.\" Not a lesser thing, not a substitute. A second chance. A divine door left open.",
