    "script": "ἀποκαλύπτεται",
    "translit": "<strong>apokalyptetai</strong> · is being revealed; disclosed; uncovered",
    "title": "Apokalyptetai — Revealed/Declared",
    "description": "The resurrection is not an upgrade or a promotion. It is an unveiling. Christ&apos;s divine nature was always there. The resurrection simply removes the veil and shows us who we have been looking at all along.",
