    "title": "Mara — \"bitter\"",
    "description": "Naomi renames herself. She is no longer the woman of pleasantness. She is <em>Mara</em>—bitter. Scripture allows this kind of lament. God does not correct her or tell her to have faith. He lets her name the pain she has survived.",
