    "title": "Kalopsychos — Sound Doctrine",
    "description": "The Greek is not \"correct\" doctrine (orthos) but \"healthy\" doctrine (kalos)—the kind that produces soundness of mind and body, the kind you can actually <em>live</em>. False doctrine is a virus. Sound doctrine is medicine.",
