    "translit": "<strong>anakainōsis</strong> · renewal; restoration to newness; continuous renewal",
    "title": "Anakainōsis — Renewing",
    "description": "While palingenesia is the once-for-all birth into new life, anakainōsis is the ongoing renewal. The Holy Ghost does not touch you once and leave. He continuously renews you—mind, heart, will. Moment by moment, day by day, the Spirit refreshes your commitment to Christ.",
